                </svg>

              </h3>
              <p>You will receive an SMS once your order is ready. Enjoy!</p>
              <p><form method="get" action="/api/orders"><button type="submit" class="btn btn-light"> Review Order History </button></form></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


